{"id":254648,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-福州7冤民被囚北京黑监狱，家人请求关注/","date":"2012-10-02T17:30:58Z","modified":"2012-10-02T17:30:58Z","title":"维权网 | 福州7冤民被囚北京黑监狱，家人请求关注（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员洪宪民报道）中秋佳节期间，福州仓山区城门镇的陈寿海在煎熬中期待妻子刘玉钗能够平安归来共度中秋，一对未成年的儿女也在喊着：妈妈，我肚子饿了。</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冤民刘玉钗于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>随福州冤民保钓敢死队林炳兴、陈依香、欧中辉、张秀屏、林善忠、刘建新等人，一起乘大巴车上京去保钓。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>点，在途经天津时，遇上上百福州警察、官员等维稳大部队滥权非法打压堵截，被强行绑架到北京都鑫园招待所黑监狱非法囚禁。</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span></span><span>名保钓冤民进京途中遭非法阻截，并被限制人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>名保钓冤民都是背负天大冤屈，其中张秀屏含冤无望昭雪下曾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次在京自杀反遭劳教，刚出来没几天；陈依香也曾自焚抗强拆；林炳兴的妻子也曾经在福建省检察院前自焚抗议福州司法黑暗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本来进京保钓并未违法，况且还未开展保钓活动。保钓行为就算“触犯”《刑法》或《治安管理处罚法》，警方采取强制措施后，也应在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时之内依法书面告知家人。但家人至今都未收到有关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>名冤民遭囚禁的书面通知。</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>名冤民家人请求全社会关注他们亲人的安危。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-cEckuSbVY0Y/UGrnTFuj94I/AAAAAAAAQMk/WltRwakCaz8/s1600/%E8%BF%9B%E4%BA%AC%E4%BF%9D%E9%92%935.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-cEckuSbVY0Y/UGrnTFuj94I/AAAAAAAAQMk/WltRwakCaz8/s320/%E8%BF%9B%E4%BA%AC%E4%BF%9D%E9%92%935.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>进京保钓冤民<span> </span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4ZmlwkpVRaA/UGrnUXP6OtI/AAAAAAAAQMs/qfrSUAd2pBc/s1600/%E5%88%98%E7%8E%89%E9%92%97%E5%BD%92%E6%9D%A5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"220\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4ZmlwkpVRaA/UGrnUXP6OtI/AAAAAAAAQMs/qfrSUAd2pBc/s320/%E5%88%98%E7%8E%89%E9%92%97%E5%BD%92%E6%9D%A5.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4537989698981090502?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}